<h3 id="2-call-your-friends">2. Call your friends</h3>

<p>Every Saturday evening, I hangout with my friends in church with <em>zoom or skype</em> just to check in with each other. It is a great way to relax and just socialize.</p>

<p>Remember to wear a mask when you are going outside. It is very important especially these days, as the corona virus is deadly ü¶†.</p>

